INSERT INTO alerts_historical (
                alert_id,
                machine_id,
                organization_id,
                client_id,
                node_name,
                created_at,
                acknowledged_at,
                resolved_at,
                alert_data
            )
            VALUES (
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7,
                now(),
                $8
            )
